Revision history for Template-Plugin-MultiMarkdown
==================================================

0.12    2015-04-04
        - removed duplicate key 'build_requires' from META.

0.11    2015-01-05
        - fixed license fields in META.json to be lists.

0.10    2014-08-15
        - added runtime recommends prerequisite.
        - added LICENSE file.

0.09    2014-08-09
        - require a more stable, and heavily bugfixed version of
          Text::MultiMarkdown. This also includes all the newer features.
        - inserted missing test->requires/recommends section in META.json.
        - added missing FindBin prerequisite.
        - extract release test scripts from distribution, now in git only.

0.08    2014-06-30
        - fixed prerequisite versions.

0.07    2014-06-29
        - new maintainer: BARBIE.
        - change file dates changed to meet W3CDTF standards.
        - reworked META files.
        - reworked Makefile.PL for clarity.
        - reworked README.
        - revised and extended test suite.
        - added git repository links to metadata.

0.06    2013-06-22
        - Added dependency on parent

0.04    2013-06-21
        - Added code to use Text::MultiMarkdown:XS if it is available

0.03    2009-03-03T20:29:30
        - added dependency on Template

0.02    2009-03-02T20:46:03
        - added proper "kwalitee" tests and generally tidied up distribution

0.01    2008-03-24T17:06:40
	    - original version - based on Template::Plugin::Markdown
